data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom move-in-ready home is nestled in the well-established Meadowood community in Garland. You'll appreciate the flexibility provided by the Garland Independent School District, allowing you to choose your preferred school. This residence boasts an inviting open concept design. The kitchen is modern and stylish, featuring contemporary paint and lighting, as well as generous cabinet and counter space. You can enjoy meals in the eat-in kitchen or utilize the separate yet practical dining room.  Ascend to the upper level, where you'll discover three spacious bedrooms, with the primary bedroom showcasing a sizable walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom.  Unwind on the open patio in the fully fenced private backyard, complete with an inviting pool for hosting your guests. Conveniently, the two-car garage is situated at the rear of the home with alley access.  Conveniently situated close to shopping, dining, and just 20 miles from Downtown Dallas.
